    <layout-text>
      <p>A centered login form using <code>data-layout="cover"</code> on the body for vertical centering, with <code>&lt;layout-card&gt;</code> constraining the width. The form itself uses <code>data-layout="stack"</code> for vertical spacing.</p>
    </layout-text>

